{"type":"message","id":"ef00e583","parentId":"39f7a0dd","timestamp":"2026-04-27T20:21:02.624Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The query parser is having issues with the subject containing spaces. Let me try a different approach and just read the raw message with a different ID or approach.\n\nActually, I realize I should just look at the emails I've already read. In the email I read for ID 9 earlier (from RC Leasing), it showed the full thread including Bobby's responses. The most recent response from Bobby that was shown was:\n\n\"Good afternoon, We were hoping sometime before June 4th. I will follow up once Logan completes his portion of the application. Thank you, Robert Galletta\"\n\nThat was the April 27 email. But that was displayed as part of the thread within the email from RC Leasing. \n\nThe issue is that when I queried the sent folder, I got 4 emails from Bobby to Royal Cove, but I haven't been able to retrieve the actual message content for IDs 7 and 8 individually—I've only seen them referenced within the thread view from RC Leasing's email. Let me try accessing the message directly to get the actual full email content.","thinkingSignature":"4d97d769a82b231e623a1da3ce3681f5fded01b55c267090ff5edd182ac7b606"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_74ei1x0w40q0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"himalaya message read --account icloud --mailbox \"Sent Messages\" -- 8 2>&1","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":14967,"output":273,"cacheRead":25228,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40468,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777321255005,"responseId":"063ef8270552346caff6e74690627477"}}
