{"type":"message","id":"9be1a855","parentId":"b1d0ef74","timestamp":"2026-04-27T20:21:50.437Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is saying the most recent email he sent is what he's looking for. Let me check the sent folder again for the most recent email from his iCloud account.","thinkingSignature":"1ff23c2828acc5401e6d2a2cf00438280779dd7c34f348f2ad49e23787bbebf4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5fbdfa246917_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"himalaya message read --account icloud -- 8 2>&1","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":146,"output":84,"cacheRead":25228,"cacheWrite":9265,"totalTokens":34723,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777321188430,"responseId":"063ef7e559cba72cf5b04d6d5c50d869"}}
{"type":"message","id":"baccb6a2","parentId":"9be1a855","timestamp":"2026-04-27T20:21:50.437Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5fbdfa246917_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[2m2026-04-27T20:19:53.335804Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T20:19:53.336431Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T20:19:53.336452Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T20:19:53.336496Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\nFrom: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHi Amy, I wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part o\nReport This Email<removed-link>\n\n\nHi Amy,\n\n\n\nI wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part of the application on his end.\n\n\n\nWe are still very interested in a 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom unit. Please let me know if you need anything else from me in the meantime, or if there are any updates on availability.\n\n\n\nThank you,\n\nRobert Galletta\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/Outlook-A picture .png\"><#/part>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":951,"aggregated":"[2m2026-04-27T20:19:53.335804Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T20:19:53.336431Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T20:19:53.336452Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T20:19:53.336496Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\nFrom: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHi Amy, I wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part o\nReport This Email<removed-link>\n\n\nHi Amy,\n\n\n\nI wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part of the application on his end.\n\n\n\nWe are still very interested in a 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom unit. Please let me know if you need anything else from me in the meantime, or if there are any updates on availability.\n\n\n\nThank you,\n\nRobert Galletta\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/Outlook-A picture .png\"><#/part>","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777321193597}}
{"type":"message","id":"8b5935b9","parentId":"baccb6a2","timestamp":"2026-04-27T20:21:50.437Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Hmm, that's still the April 25 email. But there was one more recent sent email - ID 8 was from RC Leasing TO Bobby, not from Bobby TO RC. Let me check - the sent folder list showed:\n- ID 8 was from rtg.bobby@icloud.com - \"Re: Looking for new apartment\" - 2026-04-27 16:02\n- ID 7 was from rtg.bobby@icloud.com - \"Re: Looking for new apartment\" - 2026-04-27 12:17\n\nWait, ID 8 in the sent folder is actually the most recent SENT email from Bobby. Let me read it.","thinkingSignature":"5ad5153e22c9ac40dad0cee6a2439dcdc7c5d38ddfb932df3d780a5077e5d960"},{"type":"text","text":"That's ID 8 being listed as received, but let me get your actual most recent sent email (ID 7 from April 27 at 12:17 PM):\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zfm07n5swwhg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"himalaya message read --account icloud -- 7 2>&1","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":10105,"output":226,"cacheRead":25228,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35559,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777321193600,"responseId":"063ef7e9fa267f78f777bf20d80cba69"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0997861e","parentId":"8b5935b9","timestamp":"2026-04-27T20:21:50.437Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zfm07n5swwhg_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[2m2026-04-27T20:20:00.579496Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T20:20:00.579588Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T20:20:00.579603Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T20:20:00.579653Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\nFrom: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: Bobby Galletta <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nThank you for your interest in Royal Cove! Offering affordable Apartments located in the Town of Poughkeepsie.\nKindly Note: Availability is subject to change throughout the inquiry process.\n1 Bedroom/ 1 Bath starting at $1825.00\n2 Bedroom/ 1 Bath starting at $2150.00\n3 Bedroom/ 1 Bath starting at $2595.00\n\nOnsite Amenities:\nExterior amenities include a swimming pool, playground areas, picnic & grill areas, dog parks and basketball court. Interior amenities include laundry room on site, fully renovated  units, business center, lounge area and fitness center.\nUtilities:\nHeat ,Hot water, garbage, sewer, landscaping, etc. are included.  Electric, cable and internet are additional and paid for by tenants.\nWhat you need to know before applying!\nPet Friendly! One-time pet fee: $400 per dog & $200 per cat. Monthly Pet Rent is $35 per Dog & $25 per cat. No aggressive breeds (Rottweilers, Pit-Bulls, German Shepherds, Dobermans, Chows, etc.).  At full maturity they cannot weigh more than 50lbs. 2 pet maximum.\nOur leases are for 1 year.\n$20 application fee per adult (non-refundable).  All adults residing in the unit must be screened.  The screening process will consist of a credit check, background check, and mandatory pet screening .  You must provide your full social security number for the screening process.\nTotal household NET income 2.5 times the monthly rent is required.    We look for a credit score of 600 or higher\nRhino Partner- Rhino Policies start as low as $9 per month*, compared to an upfront cash deposit.\nAs required per the lease agreement all new tenants will be enrolled in the Waiver Program at an additional $18 per month. Ask us how this program benefits you!\nSpectrum through the property rep starting at $49.99 a month\nPlease let us know if you have already applied to our sister properties: Royal Ledges Aor Royal Gardens\n\n\n\n\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com<https://shared.outlook.inky.com/link?domain=royalcoveapts.com&t=h.eJx1jUEOwiAURK_SsLalvyjQrrwKhQ82YiGUGhvj3YWNO3cvmTczb7InT6aG3HKOE6UpHMrr8EQV89bp8CCnhtyr4PG1rC6HtY0pREz5aF0Ke6RJe1Rbya4_Jbpapb1AaSSCGJjl1poLH80ZJGih55kPQEGIXgLvGe-AyXEU9Q3r29_RaphirLv3BZeC8PkCt98_GQ.MEUCIQCWTK6waHQ5m4oXXmmk0HWUWuJpREFHCvC4dLlg9W3LSQIgBWmuktwnm5U9QNOCLRJfbL_fBqb8ylv8lngBFhSNwTY>\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: Bobby Galletta <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Monday, April 13, 2026 11:12 AM\nTo: RC Leasing <rcleasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Looking for new apartment\n\n Hello, I hope you’re doing well. My partner Logan and I are currently searching for a 1-bedroom apartment and are looking to move in by early June, ideally before June 6. We are relocating from Tenn\n[cid:inky-injection-inliner-03755809cc10337ec572b1f12a6beedf]\nCaution: External (rtg.bobby@icloud.com<mailto:rtg.bobby@icloud.com>)\nFirst-Time Sender   Details<removed-link>\n[cid:inky-injection-inliner-97c0836b41e87f6018b00b7d2e96af51]\n  Report This Email<removed-link>\n\n Hello,\n\n\nI hope you’re doing well. My partner Logan and I are currently searching for a 1-bedroom apartment and are looking to move in by early June, ideally before June 6.\n\n\nWe are relocating from Tennessee, and I do plan to come up in person to tour the apartment before moving.\n\n\nWe do have a dog named Finnly who is about 50 lbs, so we would also like to know about your pet policies, including any associated fees or restrictions.\n\n\nAdditionally, could you please provide details on what would be required upfront to secure a unit? Specifically, we’re interested in understanding the security deposit, any application or administrative fees, pet fees, and any other initial costs.\n\n\nCould you also let us know if you currently have any 1-bedroom units available, or if you expect any availability to open up before June 6?\n\n\nLastly, are you currently offering any move-in specials or promotions?\n\n\nThank you for your time, and we look forward to hearing from you.\n\n\nBest regards,\n\nRobert Galletta\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/image.png\"><#/part>\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/Outlook-A picture .png\"><#/part>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2033,"aggregated":"[2m2026-04-27T20:20:00.579496Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T20:20:00.579588Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T20:20:00.579603Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T20:20:00.579653Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\nFrom: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: Bobby Galletta <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nThank you for your interest in Royal Cove! Offering affordable Apartments located in the Town of Poughkeepsie.\nKindly Note: Availability is subject to change throughout the inquiry process.\n1 Bedroom/ 1 Bath starting at $1825.00\n2 Bedroom/ 1 Bath starting at $2150.00\n3 Bedroom/ 1 Bath starting at $2595.00\n\nOnsite Amenities:\nExterior amenities include a swimming pool, playground areas, picnic & grill areas, dog parks and basketball court. Interior amenities include laundry room on site, fully renovated  units, business center, lounge area and fitness center.\nUtilities:\nHeat ,Hot water, garbage, sewer, landscaping, etc. are included.  Electric, cable and internet are additional and paid for by tenants.\nWhat you need to know before applying!\nPet Friendly! One-time pet fee: $400 per dog & $200 per cat. Monthly Pet Rent is $35 per Dog & $25 per cat. No aggressive breeds (Rottweilers, Pit-Bulls, German Shepherds, Dobermans, Chows, etc.).  At full maturity they cannot weigh more than 50lbs. 2 pet maximum.\nOur leases are for 1 year.\n$20 application fee per adult (non-refundable).  All adults residing in the unit must be screened.  The screening process will consist of a credit check, background check, and mandatory pet screening .  You must provide your full social security number for the screening process.\nTotal household NET income 2.5 times the monthly rent is required.    We look for a credit score of 600 or higher\nRhino Partner- Rhino Policies start as low as $9 per month*, compared to an upfront cash deposit.\nAs required per the lease agreement all new tenants will be enrolled in the Waiver Program at an additional $18 per month. Ask us how this program benefits you!\nSpectrum through the property rep starting at $49.99 a month\nPlease let us know if you have already applied to our sister properties: Royal Ledges Aor Royal Gardens\n\n\n\n\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com<https://shared.outlook.inky.com/link?domain=royalcoveapts.com&t=h.eJx1jUEOwiAURK_SsLalvyjQrrwKhQ82YiGUGhvj3YWNO3cvmTczb7InT6aG3HKOE6UpHMrr8EQV89bp8CCnhtyr4PG1rC6HtY0pREz5aF0Ke6RJe1Rbya4_Jbpapb1AaSSCGJjl1poLH80ZJGih55kPQEGIXgLvGe-AyXEU9Q3r29_RaphirLv3BZeC8PkCt98_GQ.MEUCIQCWTK6waHQ5m4oXXmmk0HWUWuJpREFHCvC4dLlg9W3LSQIgBWmuktwnm5U9QNOCLRJfbL_fBqb8ylv8lngBFhSNwTY>\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: Bobby Galletta <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Monday, April 13, 2026 11:12 AM\nTo: RC Leasing <rcleasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Looking for new apartment\n\n Hello, I hope you’re doing well. My partner Logan and I are currently searching for a 1-bedroom apartment and are looking to move in by early June, ideally before June 6. We are relocating from Tenn\n[cid:inky-injection-inliner-03755809cc10337ec572b1f12a6beedf]\nCaution: External (rtg.bobby@icloud.com<mailto:rtg.bobby@icloud.com>)\nFirst-Time Sender   Details<removed-link>\n[cid:inky-injection-inliner-97c0836b41e87f6018b00b7d2e96af51]\n  Report This Email<removed-link>\n\n Hello,\n\n\nI hope you’re doing well. My partner Logan and I are currently searching for a 1-bedroom apartment and are looking to move in by early June, ideally before June 6.\n\n\nWe are relocating from Tennessee, and I do plan to come up in person to tour the apartment before moving.\n\n\nWe do have a dog named Finnly who is about 50 lbs, so we would also like to know about your pet policies, including any associated fees or restrictions.\n\n\nAdditionally, could you please provide details on what would be required upfront to secure a unit? Specifically, we’re interested in understanding the security deposit, any application or administrative fees, pet fees, and any other initial costs.\n\n\nCould you also let us know if you currently have any 1-bedroom units available, or if you expect any availability to open up before June 6?\n\n\nLastly, are you currently offering any move-in specials or promotions?\n\n\nThank you for your time, and we look forward to hearing from you.\n\n\nBest regards,\n\nRobert Galletta\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/image.png\"><#/part>\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/Outlook-A picture .png\"><#/part>","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777321201824}}
{"type":"message","id":"53ab9466","parentId":"0997861e","timestamp":"2026-04-27T20:21:50.437Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"That's ID 7 which is from RC Leasing TO Bobby, showing the conversation. Bobby's actual sent emails were ID 8 and ID 7 in the sent folder list. Let me look at the sent folder list again. Wait, the sent folder shows:\n\n```\n| 8  |       | Re: Looking for new apartment         | rtg.bobby@icloud.com | 2026-04-27 16:02-04:00 |\n| 7  |       | Re: Looking for new apartment         | rtg.bobby@icloud.com | 2026-04-27 12:17-04:00 |\n| 6  |       | Re: Looking for new apartment         | Robert Galletta      | 2026-04-25 17:54+00:00 |\n\n\n| 5  |       | Looking for new apartment             | Bobby Galletta       | 2026-04-13 11:12-04:00 |\n```\n\nSo ID 8 at 4:02 PM and ID 7 at 12:17 PM are Bobby's most recent sent emails about Royal Cove. ID 8 was the 4:02 PM one I already read, and ID 7 at 12:17 PM is the one starting with \"Good afternoon, We were hoping sometime before...\"\n\nI need to re-examine the himalaya output more carefully. When I queried the sent folder, ID 7 showed as coming from rtg.bobby@icloud.com with the subject \"Re: Looking for new apartment\" dated 2026-04-27 12:17-04:00, which means it was sent at 12:17 PM Eastern time that same day.\n\nHowever, when I called `himalaya message read --account icloud -- 7`, it returned a completely different message - a long email from RC Leasing about Royal Cove's amenities and pricing. This suggests there might be a mismatch between the envelope IDs in the sent folder listing and the actual message IDs in the mailbox. The envelope ID 7 from the sent folder search doesn't correspond to message ID 7 when I read it directly. I should check ID 8 to see if it's also misaligned, though I'm realizing the IDs in himalaya represent envelope identifiers rather than message sequence numbers, so the read command might need a different approach to fetch the actual sent messages.","thinkingSignature":"8d850a525d64f19dbdb1d66fdf9148f1fc1919636c0c44313aca65106c9a29d3"},{"type":"text","text":"Let me try reading ID 8 from your sent folder:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6hhkx6crdks7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"himalaya envelope thread --account icloud --folder \"Sent Messages\" -- 8 2>&1","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":11834,"output":561,"cacheRead":25228,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37623,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777321201828,"responseId":"063ef7f156e4f902251a1b0e7a8e9442"}}
