{"type":"message","id":"57e8ce9f","parentId":"ff5e16e5","timestamp":"2026-04-27T20:23:24.036Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Hmm, the message read command doesn't support -o json for reading individual messages. Let me try a different approach. The issue might be that himalaya is showing the thread view, which starts with the most recent message in the thread (which is from RC Leasing, since they're threaded together).\n\nLet me try to figure out if there's a way to get the actual raw message. Maybe I should look at the full raw email source. Let me try a different approach.","thinkingSignature":"71b6c82b83d5ecd570e9ffcb4dc378738a01fa8bb8a4fdfca1eac0c7e18d1a7f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_k3yfmzrdoum2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"himalaya message read --account icloud -- 8 --full 2>&1 | grep -v \"^\\[2m\\|^\\[9[0-9]m\\|_WARN\\|imap_codec\\|Rectified\" | head -100","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":16352,"output":181,"cacheRead":25228,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41761,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777321383185,"responseId":"063ef8a7a750403cb0b12793d45377f1"}}
